<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="C" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Club" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Club,</orth> a heavy stick: <cit><quote>Hercules' c.</quote> <bibl n="shak. ado 2.1.262" default="NO" valid="yes">Ado II, 1, 262</bibl></cit>. <bibl n="shak. ado 3.3.147" default="NO" valid="yes">III, 3, 147</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. lll 1.2.182" default="NO" valid="yes">LLL I, 2, 182</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. lll 5.1.139" default="NO" valid="yes">V, 1, 139</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. lll 5.2.593" default="NO" valid="yes">V, 2, 593</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. ant 4.12.46" default="NO" valid="yes">Ant. IV, 12, 46</bibl>. <cit><quote>a Grecian c.</quote> <bibl n="shak. ayl 4.1.98" default="NO" valid="yes">As IV, 1, 98</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>bats and --s</quote> <bibl n="shak. cor 1.1.57" default="NO" valid="yes">Cor. I, 1, 57</bibl></cit>. <bibl n="shak. cor 1.1.57" default="NO" valid="yes">Cor. I, 1, 57</bibl> <bibl n="shak. rom 4.3.54" default="NO" valid="yes">Rom. IV, 3, 54</bibl>. -- In any public affray, the cry was <emph>Clubs! Clubs!</emph> by way of calling for persons with clubs to part the combatants (Nares): <bibl n="shak. ayl 5.2.44" default="NO" valid="yes">As V, 2, 44</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 1h6 1.3.84" default="NO" valid="yes">H6A I, 3, 84</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. h8 5.4.53" default="NO" valid="yes">H8 V, 4, 53</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. tit 2.1.37" default="NO" valid="yes">Tit. II, 1, 37</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. rom 1.1.80" default="NO" valid="yes">Rom. I, 1, 80</bibl>.
</entryFree></div1></body></text></TEI.2>